<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="ko">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <meta http-equiv="X-UA-Compatible" content="ie=edge">
  <title>SOOY-K CRM</title>
  <link href="/css/styles.css" rel="stylesheet">
  <style>
    .landing-container {
      min-height: 100vh;
      display: flex;
      flex-direction: column;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: center;
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, #f5f7fa 0%, #c3cfe2 100%);
      padding: 20px;
    }
    
    .logo-container {
      margin-bottom: 2rem;
      text-align: center;
    }
    
    .logo-container img {
      max-width: 200px;
      margin-bottom: 1rem;
    }
    
    .title {
      font-size: 2.5rem;
      font-weight: bold;
      color: #2c3e50;
      margin-bottom: 1rem;
      text-align: center;
    }
    
    .subtitle {
      font-size: 1.2rem;
      color: #34495e;
      margin-bottom: 2rem;
      text-align: center;
      max-width: 600px;
    }
    
    .buttons-container {
      display: flex;
      gap: 1rem;
      margin-top: 2rem;
    }
    
    .btn-try-free {
      background-color: #4CAF50;
      color: white;
      padding: 12px 30px;
      border-radius: 25px;
      text-decoration: none;
      font-weight: bold;
      transition: background-color 0.3s;
    }
    
    .btn-try-free:hover {
      background-color: #45a049;
    }
    
    .btn-sign-in {
      background-color: transparent;
      color: #2c3e50;
      padding: 12px 30px;
      border-radius: 25px;
      text-decoration: none;
      font-weight: bold;
      border: 2px solid #2c3e50;
      transition: all 0.3s;
    }
    
    .btn-sign-in:hover {
      background-color: #2c3e50;
      color: white;
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="landing-container">
    <div class="logo-container">
      <h1 class="title">Simple CRM</h1>
      <p class="subtitle">
        고객 관리의 새로운 기준, Simple CRM과 함께 비즈니스를 성장시키세요.
        간편한 사용성과 강력한 기능으로 당신의 비즈니스를 한 단계 더 발전시킬 수 있습니다.
      </p>
    </div>
    
    <div class="buttons-container">
      <a href="/client/login" class="btn-try-free">Try Free</a>
      <a href="/user/login" class="btn-sign-in">Sign In</a>
    </div>
  </div>

  <script src="/util/util.js"></script>
</body>
</html>